    10004 [label=<BlueOakCouncil: <B><FONT COLOR="/svg/black">Bronze</FONT></B><BR />These licenses lack important but nonessential elements of permissive open<BR />software licenses or impose additional requirements or restrictions, such as<BR />BSD-style prohibitions against endorsement and promotion.>
